                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290910-284-off1565 t18290910-284-crimeloc1567"></join>, 28 pieces of foreign gold coin called Napoleons, value 22l., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290910-284-victim2655" type="victimName">
